#8-5. Cities
def describe_city(city, country="United States"):
    print(f"{city.title()} is in {country.title()}.")

describe_city("Athens")
describe_city("Atlanta")
describe_city("San Jose", "Costa Rica")
Athens is in United States.
Atlanta is in United States.
San Jose is in Costa Rica.
